                      </div>
                      <div class="flex items-center">
                        <span class="pulse-dot w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                        <span class="text-red-600 font-semibold"><%= currentStreamStatus.toUpperCase() %></span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                <% } else { %>
                  <div class="video-preview p-8 text-center text-gray-500">
                    <i class="fas fa-video text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                    <p class="text-lg font-medium">No stream configured</p>
                    <p class="text-sm">Add embed code above to activate this stream</p>
                  </div>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Instructions -->
        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fas fa-broadcast-tower text-yellow-600 mt-1 mr-3 text-xl"></i>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-yellow-800 mb-3">üî¥ Live Streaming Instructions:</h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">üì∫ Supported Platforms:</h5>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>YouTube Live:</strong> Best for official tournaments</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Facebook Live:</strong> Great for community engagement</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Twitch:</strong> Popular for gaming tournaments</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Vimeo Live:</strong> Professional streaming</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Custom RTMP:</strong> Any streaming service</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h5 class="font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-2">‚öôÔ∏è Setup Tips:</h5>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-yellow-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Set stream status to match actual broadcast</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Test embed codes before going live</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Use descriptive titles for each stream</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Configure maximum streams based on needs</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Update tournament title for branding</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-red-100 border border-red-300 rounded-lg">
                <h5 class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800 mb-2">üö® Troubleshooting:</h5>
                <ul class="text-xs text-red-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Stream not showing:</strong> Check if embed code includes proper iframe tags</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>YouTube Live blocked:</strong> Ensure channel has live streaming enabled</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Facebook Live issues:</strong> Verify privacy settings allow embedding</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Audio/Video sync:</strong> Contact streaming platform support</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('../../partials/footer') %>
